        <hl1>QUOTATION OF THE DAY</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''We've done pretty well. But we could be doing much better. I've heard some people refer to it as the rule of halves. Half the people who need to be treated are treated and half who are treated are adequately treated.''</p>
        <p>DR. ELIZABETH NABEL, director of the National Heart, Lung and Blood Institute, on the treatment of heart disease. [20]</p>
      </block>
